 history, and triggers a‚Ä¶","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-26-client-workflow-requirements.md\",\"‚Ä¶","timestamp":"2026-06-27T02:57:29.092Z","title":"Edit","type":"file_edit"},"sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","type":"compressed"},"obs_mqvrryoq_97853e873023":{"observation":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":["/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-26-client-workflow-requirements.md"],"id":"obs_mqvrryoq_97853e873023","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-26-client-workflow-requirements.md\",\"new_string\":\"## Open Questions\\n\\n_All open questions resolved during requirements review._\",\"old_string\":\"## Open Questions\\n\\n- OQ-1: Should the workflow dashboard show only the **most recent** engagement per client, or allow showing all years (with a year filter)?\\n- OQ-2: Wha‚Ä¶","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-26-client-workflow-requirements.md\",\"‚Ä¶","timestamp":"2026-06-27T02:57:36.568Z","title":"Edit","type":"file_edit"},"sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","type":"compressed"},"obs_mqvrs5xm_271fd5363765":{"observation":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":["/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-26-client-workflow-requirements.md"],"id":"obs_mqvrs5xm_271fd5363765","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-26-client-workflow-requirements.md\",\"new_string\":\"## Data Model\\n\\n**Additions to `clients` table (V13 migration):**\\n```\\nbusiness_type            VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL   -- PERSONAL | CORPORATE | SELF_EMPLOYED\\nfiscal_year_end_month    SMALLINT NULL       